curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/4758' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM8558-2XG", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM8558-2XG is a dual, low noise, high precision  CMOS operational amplifier that provides a high output  current of 230mA, rail-to-rail output operation from a  range of 2.8V to 5.5V single supply.   The SGM8558-2XG offers low input offset voltage, low  input offset voltage drift and high output current drive.  The device also can achieve a high 15MHz  gain-bandwidth product and a high 8V/μs slew rate.   The SGM8558-2XG is specifically designed to drive  high current load, such as 32Ω headset, VBIAS of RF  power amplifier, etc.  The  SGM8558-2XG  is  available  in  a  Green  WLCSP-1.45×1.45-8B package. It operates over an  ambient temperature range of -40℃ to +125℃.       "}'
